#message:28:006
{
	[Color:18]Goombarius is a legendary[BR]
	Goomba trying to get laid.[BR]
	He owns the latest smartphones[BR]
	and video game consoles.[BR]
	Press [C-DOWN] to have him tell you[BR]
	about everything nearby.[BR]
	He has no filter, so he says[BR]
	whatever's on his mind.[BR]
	His specialty is checking rizz.[BR]
	He's very good at that.[End]
}

