#message:28:013
{
	[Color:18]A super cool Koopa with a[BR]
	nack for adventuring.[BR]
	He gets embarrassed easily,[BR]
	but always loves to show off.[BR]
	Press [C-DOWN] to shoot out his shell[BR]
	to grab items or hit objects.[BR]
	He can also first strike enemies[BR]
	with his shell.[BR]
	In combat he can attack all[BR]
	enemies on the ground.[End]
}

